-- Palestinian Gunman Killed in Northern Gaza by Israeli Fire, Official Says
-- B y   G w e n   A c k e r m a n
-- 2010-10-27T10:43:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-27/palestinian-gunman-killed-in-northern-gaza-by-israeli-fire-official-says.html
A Palestinian gunman was killed by
Israeli fire in the northern part of the Gaza Strip today, Adham
Abu Selmeya, a spokesman for medical services said by phone.
Saraya al-Quds, a Gaza group, said the man was killed while
carrying out “a military mission.”  An Israeli army spokeswoman said she was checking reports
of the incident.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Gwen Ackerman in Jerusalem at 
 gackerman@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
